{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "p5br0yhkzkk",
    "category": "movie",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p5BR0YHKZkk",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I had another argument with my landlady this morning.",
      "zh": "我今天早上又和房東吵架了。",
      "ja": "今朝、また大家さんと口論したんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What happened?",
      "zh": "發生什麼事了？",
      "ja": "どうしたの？",
      "time": "00:00:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, it was about money.",
      "zh": "嗯，是關於錢的事。",
      "ja": "ええ、お金のことなんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "She wants to raise the rent.",
      "zh": "她想要調高房租。",
      "ja": "家賃を上げたいって言ってるんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "She wants $400 a month.",
      "zh": "她想要每個月400美元。",
      "ja": "月に400ドルにしたいんだって。",
      "time": "00:00:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Angie, that's too much money.",
      "zh": "Angie，那太多錢了。",
      "ja": "アンジー、それは多すぎるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I know.",
      "zh": "我知道。",
      "ja": "わかってるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I told her the same thing.",
      "zh": "我也跟她說了一樣的話。",
      "ja": "同じことを彼女に言ったんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I have an idea that may help you.",
      "zh": "我有個主意可能能幫助你。",
      "ja": "君の役に立つかもしれないアイデアがあるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, really?",
      "zh": "喔，真的嗎？",
      "ja": "本当？",
      "time": "00:00:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And what is that?",
      "zh": "是什麼呢？",
      "ja": "それは何？",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, I was thinking of doing this too.",
      "zh": "嗯，我也在想做這件事。",
      "ja": "ええ、私もそれをしようと思っていたんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Why don't we get some part-time jobs and then earn some more money?",
      "zh": "我們為什麼不找些兼職工作，然後賺更多錢呢？",
      "ja": "パートタイムの仕事をして、もっとお金を稼いだらどう？",
      "time": "00:00:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We have some extra time on the weekends.",
      "zh": "我們週末有些空閒時間。",
      "ja": "週末に少し余裕があるしね。",
      "time": "00:00:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, that is certainly worth trying.",
      "zh": "嗯，這確實值得嘗試。",
      "ja": "それは確かに試す価値があるね。",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you want to go and fill out applications after work?",
      "zh": "你想下班後去填申請表嗎？",
      "ja": "仕事の後に応募用紙を書きに行く？",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sure.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "もちろん。",
      "time": "00:00:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's not waste any time.",
      "zh": "別浪費時間了。",
      "ja": "時間を無駄にしないでおこう。",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's get busy.",
      "zh": "開始行動吧。",
      "ja": "さあ、始めよう。",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Great.",
      "zh": "太好了。",
      "ja": "いいね。",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's meet after work.",
      "zh": "下班後見。",
      "ja": "仕事の後に会おう。",
      "time": "00:00:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Check, please.",
      "zh": "請結帳。",
      "ja": "お会計お願いします。",
      "time": "00:00:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "OK, let's see.",
      "zh": "好，讓我看看。",
      "ja": "よし、見てみよう。",
      "time": "00:01:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This application form wants my name.",
      "zh": "這份申請表要我的名字。",
      "ja": "この応募用紙は名前を求めている。",
      "time": "00:01:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Angie Roberts.",
      "zh": "Angie Roberts。",
      "ja": "アンジー・ロバーツ。",
      "time": "00:01:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No problem.",
      "zh": "沒問題。",
      "ja": "問題ないよ。",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Next, my address.",
      "zh": "接著是我的地址。",
      "ja": "次は住所だ。",
      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "16 new lifts, three.",
      "zh": "16 new lifts，三號。",
      "ja": "16ニューリフト、3。",
      "time": "00:01:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Apartment 7 is stumble.",
      "zh": "7號公寓是stumble。",
      "ja": "7号室はスタンブル。",
      "time": "00:01:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah, my phone number.",
      "zh": "啊，我的電話號碼。",
      "ja": "ああ、電話番号だ。",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "212-457-8367.",
      "zh": "212-457-8367。",
      "ja": "212-457-8367。",
      "time": "00:01:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now, my cell phone number.",
      "zh": "現在是我的手機號碼。",
      "ja": "次は携帯番号。",
      "time": "00:01:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "0-5-3-3-4-5-5-6-7-7.",
      "zh": "0-5-3-3-4-5-5-6-7-7。",
      "ja": "0-5-3-3-4-5-5-6-7-7。",
      "time": "00:01:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's see.",
      "zh": "讓我看看。",
      "ja": "さてと。",
      "time": "00:01:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How old am I?",
      "zh": "我幾歲了？",
      "ja": "私は何歳だっけ？",
      "time": "00:01:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "72.",
      "zh": "72歲。",
      "ja": "72歳。",
      "time": "00:01:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不是。",
      "ja": "違うよ。",
      "time": "00:01:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just kidding.",
      "zh": "開玩笑的。",
      "ja": "冗談だよ。",
      "time": "00:01:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "25.",
      "zh": "25歲。",
      "ja": "25歳。",
      "time": "00:01:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now for my tax number.",
      "zh": "現在是我的稅號。",
      "ja": "次は税番号。",
      "time": "00:01:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "0-7-6-4-2-8-7-9-9.",
      "zh": "0-7-6-4-2-8-7-9-9。",
      "ja": "0-7-6-4-2-8-7-9-9。",
      "time": "00:01:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Email us next.",
      "zh": "接著是電子郵件。",
      "ja": "次はメールアドレス。",
      "time": "00:01:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Angie, are at Yahoo.com.",
      "zh": "Angie，are在Yahoo.com。",
      "ja": "Angie、are@Yahoo.com。",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now they want my height and weight.",
      "zh": "現在他們要我的身高和體重。",
      "ja": "今度は身長と体重を求められている。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I hate this part.",
      "zh": "我討厭這部分。",
      "ja": "この部分は嫌いだ。",
      "time": "00:01:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, 167 centimeters tall.",
      "zh": "嗯，身高167公分。",
      "ja": "ええ、身長は167センチです。",
      "time": "00:02:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And the other part?",
      "zh": "那體重呢？",
      "ja": "体重は？",
      "time": "00:02:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "On a good day, 57 kilos.",
      "zh": "狀況好的時候，57公斤。",
      "ja": "調子がいい日は57キロ。",
      "time": "00:02:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But if I've had ice cream, 60 kilos.",
      "zh": "但如果吃了冰淇淋，就是60公斤。",
      "ja": "でもアイスクリームを食べたら60キロになる。",
      "time": "00:02:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, my application asks for the same personal information.",
      "zh": "嗯，我的申請表也要求相同的個人資訊。",
      "ja": "私の応募用紙も同じ個人情報を求めているよ。",
      "time": "00:02:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Name, address, phone number, tax number, cell phone, email, age.",
      "zh": "名字、地址、電話號碼、稅號、手機、電子郵件、年齡。",
      "ja": "名前、住所、電話番号、税番号、携帯電話、メール、年齢。",
      "time": "00:02:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This one even asks for my family information.",
      "zh": "這份甚至還要我的家庭資料。",
      "ja": "これは家族情報まで求めているよ。",
      "time": "00:02:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's see.",
      "zh": "讓我看看。",
      "ja": "見てみよう。",
      "time": "00:02:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Father, work, cell phone.",
      "zh": "父親、工作、手機。",
      "ja": "父、仕事、携帯電話。",
      "time": "00:02:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Mother is a housewife.",
      "zh": "母親是家庭主婦。",
      "ja": "母は専業主婦。",
      "time": "00:02:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Three brothers, one sister.",
      "zh": "三個兄弟，一個姊妹。",
      "ja": "兄弟が3人、姉妹が1人。",
      "time": "00:02:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There's, there's surely a lot of information.",
      "zh": "這，這確實是很多資訊。",
      "ja": "情報がたくさんあるね。",
      "time": "00:02:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, my girl's done.",
      "zh": "嗯，我的填好了。",
      "ja": "ええ、私のは終わったよ。",
      "time": "00:02:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How about you?",
      "zh": "你呢？",
      "ja": "君は？",
      "time": "00:02:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, mine too.",
      "zh": "是的，我的也好了。",
      "ja": "はい、私のも終わったよ。",
      "time": "00:02:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now, tomorrow after work, we go back to the stores and businesses that we applied to and drop off these applications.",
      "zh": "明天下班後，我們回去那些申請的店家和公司，遞交申請表。",
      "ja": "明日仕事の後、応募した店や会社に戻って、これらの応募用紙を提出しよう。",
      "time": "00:02:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Maybe we can even start working by this weekend.",
      "zh": "也許我們這個週末就能開始工作。",
      "ja": "もしかしたら今週末には働き始められるかもね。",
      "time": "00:02:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Alexia, I never thought of that.",
      "zh": "Alexia，我從沒想過這點。",
      "ja": "アレクシア、それは考えたことなかった。",
      "time": "00:03:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They could need somebody, and we could be working very quickly.",
      "zh": "他們可能需要人，我們很快就能工作了。",
      "ja": "彼らは誰かを必要としているかもしれないし、すぐに働けるかもしれない。",
      "time": "00:03:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "わあ。",
      "time": "00:03:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "OK, I've got to go.",
      "zh": "好，我得走了。",
      "ja": "よし、行かなくちゃ。",
      "time": "00:03:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's almost dinner time.",
      "zh": "快到晚餐時間了。",
      "ja": "もうすぐ夕食の時間だ。",
      "time": "00:03:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "See you tomorrow at the cafe.",
      "zh": "明天咖啡廳見。",
      "ja": "明日カフェで会おう。",
      "time": "00:03:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Bye, Alexia.",
      "zh": "拜拜，Alexia。",
      "ja": "バイバイ、アレクシア。",
      "time": "00:03:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Bye.",
      "zh": "拜。",
      "ja": "バイ。",
      "time": "00:03:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Alexia, your mother tells me you might be getting an extra job soon.",
      "zh": "Alexia，你媽媽告訴我你可能很快會有兼職。",
      "ja": "アレクシア、お母さんが君がもうすぐアルバイトを始めるかもしれないって言ってたよ。",
      "time": "00:03:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is that true?",
      "zh": "是真的嗎？",
      "ja": "本当？",
      "time": "00:03:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:03:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Angie and I applied for some jobs after work.",
      "zh": "Angie和我下班後申請了一些工作。",
      "ja": "アンジーと私は仕事の後にいくつかの仕事に応募したんだ。",
      "time": "00:03:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, I think it's great you want to earn extra money.",
      "zh": "嗯，我覺得你想賺外快很棒。",
      "ja": "それは素晴らしいことだと思うよ、余分なお金を稼ぎたいなんて。",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What kind of jobs do you apply for?",
      "zh": "你們申請什麼樣的工作？",
      "ja": "どんな仕事に応募したの？",
      "time": "00:03:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, we thought about it a lot.",
      "zh": "嗯，我們想了很多。",
      "ja": "ええ、よく考えたんだ。",
      "time": "00:03:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And we thought that if we worked in clothing stores as managers of those stores, we might like working there.",
      "zh": "我們覺得如果在服裝店工作，當店經理，可能會喜歡那份工作。",
      "ja": "そして、服屋の店長として働いたら、そこが好きになるかもしれないと思ったんだ。",
      "time": "00:03:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Like Nike, Diesel, Levi's.",
      "zh": "像Nike、Diesel、Levi's。",
      "ja": "ナイキ、ディーゼル、リーバイスみたいな。",
      "time": "00:03:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's a good idea.",
      "zh": "那是個好主意。",
      "ja": "いい考えだね。",
      "time": "00:03:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I understand that if you work in the clothing stores that you mentioned, that you can get a good discount on the clothes that you buy there.",
      "zh": "我知道如果你在你提到的服裝店工作，可以買到很好的折扣。",
      "ja": "君が言った服屋で働くと、そこで買う服が割引になると聞いているよ。",
      "time": "00:04:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, that's true.",
      "zh": "是的，沒錯。",
      "ja": "はい、それは本当です。",
      "time": "00:04:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sometimes the discount is as much as 50% off the regular price.",
      "zh": "有時折扣高達五折。",
      "ja": "時には通常価格の半額になることもあるよ。",
      "time": "00:04:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, I just want to say I'm very proud of you.",
      "zh": "嗯，我只想說我很為你驕傲。",
      "ja": "うん、とにかく君をとても誇りに思っているよ。",
      "time": "00:04:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You'll learn a lot about working with customers and how businesses work.",
      "zh": "你會學到很多關於與顧客相處和商業運作的知識。",
      "ja": "お客さんと接することや、ビジネスの仕組みについて多くを学べるだろう。",
      "time": "00:04:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes, your father's right.",
      "zh": "是的，你爸爸說得對。",
      "ja": "そうだね、お父さんの言う通りだ。",
      "time": "00:04:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You'll have a lot more responsibility.",
      "zh": "你會有更多責任。",
      "ja": "もっと多くの責任を持つことになるよ。",
      "time": "00:04:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I understand, Mom, I will be careful to watch my time and not to buy too many new clothes with my new money.",
      "zh": "我知道了，媽媽，我會注意時間，也不會用新賺的錢買太多衣服。",
      "ja": "わかったよ、お母さん。時間をちゃんと管理して、新しいお金で服を買いすぎないようにするね。",
      "time": "00:04:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But it's important to remember I have even been handed in my application yet.",
      "zh": "但重要的是，我甚至還沒遞交申請表呢。",
      "ja": "でも、まだ応募用紙を提出していないことを忘れちゃいけないね。",
      "time": "00:04:28"
    }
  ]
}